# 21. Problems We Faced

### Problem 1

Backend couldn't connect to DB.

Reason

Database wasn't ready.

Solution

Added

```yaml
initContainer
```

---

### Problem 2

Database password mismatch.

Solution

Stored credentials inside Secret.

---

### Problem 3

Data disappeared after Pod deletion.

Solution

Created PVC.

---

### Problem 4

Couldn't access frontend.

Solution

Used NodePort.

---

### Problem 5

Wanted better security.

Solution

Implemented Network Policies.

